headline: Flexibility of a Home Dialysis Nurse
summary: At DaVita, we want our teammates to find the right role with flexible shifts to fit their lifestyle so they can grow their career, prioritize their well-being and reach their goals-inside and outside...

headline: 3 Reasons to Sell DVA and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Since September 2024, DaVita has been in a holding pattern, posting a small loss of 4.3% while floating around $147.02. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 3.7% gain during that period.
